data.description: Discover this stunning two-story, 4-bedroom, 2.5 bath new construction home. Its open floor plan and abundant natural light create an inviting atmosphere. The kitchen showcases elegant dark brown and quartz  countertops, and the master bedroom boasts tray ceilings and double barn doors. Enjoy the master bath with double sinks, a walk-in shower, and a separate Jacuzzi tub. Porcelain tiles grace the bathrooms, while natural vinyl plank flooring enhances the main living areas and bedrooms. Conveniently located in Dayton, with easy access to Hwy 99. Note that sod for the backyard is not included. Don't miss out on this exceptional property!
